                <p>To the Shades of the Underworld. Eunus; he lived 16 years.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" resp="#AA">
                <p>The name Eunus is familiar in Sicily from the name of the leader of the first Sicilian slave revolt (135-132 BCE), but is otherwise unattested on the island.</p>            </div>
